data.text:
Carl Braden was the current boss of West-TV. Having hate towards individuals who have powers, espically Inhumans, Braden secretly sided with the Watchdogs as a way to eliminate them. He even carried a grudge against Jessica Jones, who was responsible for putting his brother in the hospital and sought to have her killed. Braden made an attempt to kill Jones, but was ambushed by Hellcat, in which he was forced to escape. When every member of the Watchdogs were easily exposed to the public, Braden was arrested by the authorities for supporting terrorists and revealed of his deception in planning to kill Jessica Jones.
